Rating: 3
Just made this. I love Mark Bittman's "simpler than pilaf" baked rice recipe w/ mushrooms & white wine - very similar to this. However, cooking mushrooms separately on stovetop makes it a completely different, & equally delicious, pot-o-rice. White wine & evaporation gives it just enough tartness.

