I loved this. I used shitake, crimini and button mushrooms, shallots (didn't have scallions) and basmati rice. I added a little extra salt and it was so flavorful. I am always looking for alternatives to plain old boring rice and have a keeper with this one. Even my husband loved it and he is not a huge mushroom fan. Thanks!

Rating: 3
Good, but definitely needs the salt. I ended up adding soy sauce too, trying to boost the flavor. I used half plain mushrooms, half shiitake, but if I make this again, I will use a mixture of strong-flavored flavored mushrooms only. I think that's the reason the other reviewers liked this rice so much. I am thinking that changing to a more flavorful, aromatic rice would help too.

